OL,3,CDate of Makerfield by-election
OL,4,Cconfirmed
OL,6,FThe Makerfield by-election will be
OL,7,Fheld on Thursday 18 June 2026, Wigan
OL,8,FCouncil has confirmed.
OL,10,FThe by-election has been called
OL,11,Ffollowing the resignation of Josh
OL,12,FSimons MP, who stood down to allow the
OL,13,FMayor of Greater Manchester Andy
OL,14,FBurnham to stand for his seat and
OL,15,Freturn to Westminster.
OL,17,FLabour currently holds a majority of
OL,18,F5,399 in Makerfield, with Reform in
OL,19,Fsecond, with 18% of the vote.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
