OL,3,CDate of Makerfield by-election
OL,4,Cconfirmed
OL,6,FThe current Mayor of Greater
OL,7,FManchester Andy Burnham has vowed to
OL,8,Fchange the Labour party if elected,
OL,9,Famid speculation he would quickly
OL,10,Flaunch a leadership bid to challenge
OL,11,Fthe current Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,12,FStarmer.
OL,14,FThe former Leigh MP told ITV News:
OL,15,F"I'm standing on a call for change,
OL,16,Faren't I? I think we need to change
OL,17,FLabour to some degree so we can change
OL,18,Fpolitics, change the country."
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
