OL,3,CDate of Makerfield by-election
OL,4,Cconfirmed
OL,6,FHe said: "For me, we need a different
OL,7,Fpath that puts those things back under
OL,8,Fpublic control, makes them more
OL,9,Faffordable. The path that Britain has
OL,10,Fbeen on for 40 years, in my view, has
OL,11,Fbeen the wrong path.
OL,13,F"That is the main question in this by-
OL,14,Felection. Are people happy to stick on
OL,15,Fthe path that Britain's been on for 40
OL,16,Fyears, or do we want a new path?"
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
