OL,3,CDate of Makerfield by-election
OL,4,Cconfirmed
OL,6,FReform UK's candidate Robert Kenyon
OL,7,Fhas opted for a more local approach,
OL,8,Fclaiming he would become Makerfield's
OL,9,Ffirst MP to be born in the consituency
OL,10,Fif elected.
OL,12,FIn a campaign video, plumber and gas
OL,13,Fengineer Robert Kenyon said: "It get's
OL,14,Fme a bit emotional sometimes, thinking
OL,15,Fthat I could be representing people in
OL,16,FParliament. It's a massive honour.
OL,17,FPeople are going to think: hang on, he
OL,18,Fserviced my boiler last week.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
