OL,4,Cconfirmed
OL,6,F"People in this area have been taken
OL,7,Fadvantage of for too long. The
OL,8,FMakerfield constituency deserves a
OL,9,Flocal champion."
OL,11,FRestore Britain's candidate Rebecca
OL,12,FShephard has pledged to support
OL,13,Fstruggling local businesses and
OL,14,Fworking people in the constituency,
OL,15,Fwhile also highlighting her local
OL,16,Froots.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
