OL,3,CDate of Makerfield by-election
OL,4,Cconfirmed
OL,6,FA party statement said: ""Rebecca has
OL,7,Fspent most of her adult life living
OL,8,Fand working in the Wigan borough,
OL,9,Fwhere she has built and run her own
OL,10,Fsmall business.
OL,12,F"Through that experience, she
OL,13,Funderstands first-hand the pressures
OL,14,Ffacing local businesses and working
OL,15,Fpeople across the community."
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
